# This fork does NOT use API keys.
#
# All LLM work runs on your coding-agent SUBSCRIPTION (Antigravity / Gemini CLI / Claude Code) —
# the agent scores and researches directly in its own context. There is NO per-token API billing
# and NO GEMINI_API_KEY / GOOGLE_API_KEY / @google/generative-ai usage anywhere.
#
# Agents: do NOT create a .env, do NOT read or request an API key, and do NOT write a script that
# calls the Gemini/OpenAI/Anthropic API. Use the existing flow (node llm-triage.mjs --emit / --apply)
# and do the LLM scoring yourself.
#
# (No environment variables are required to run this project.)
